HEADWORD: defroster
<hw>defroster</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A device that removes ice or frost
(as from a windshield or a refrigerator or the wings of an
airplane).</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> deicer.</syn>⟦br⟧
